products.name: Canvas Cargo Pants
products.details: Relaxed-fit cargo pants in cotton canvas with straight legs. Low waist, covered elastic at sides and back of waistband, and zip fly with snap fastener. Diagonal side pockets, leg pockets with flap, and an additional pocket on one leg.

products.details: Longer, loose-fit shirt in woven fabric made from a cotton and linen blend. Collar, buttons at front, and a patch chest pocket. Dropped shoulders, long sleeves with button at cuffs, and a rounded hem.

products.name: Relaxed Fit T-shirt
products.details: Relaxed-fit T-shirt in soft cotton jersey with a printed design. Ribbed crew neck and dropped shoulders.

products.name: Nike Invincible 3
products.details: With maximum cushioning to support every mile, the Invincible 3 gives you Nike Running's highest level of comfort underfoot to help you stay on your feet today, tomorrow and beyond. Designed to help keep you on the run, it's super supportive and bouncy, so that you can propel down your preferred path and come back for your next run feeling ready and reinvigorated.

products.name: Nike Pegasus Premium
products.details: A springy ride for any run, the Peg's familiar, just-for-you feel returns to help you accomplish your goals. This version has the same responsiveness and neutral support you love but with improved comfort in those sensitive areas of your foot, like the arch and toes. Whether you're logging long marathon miles, squeezing in a speed session before the sun goes down or hopping into a spontaneous group jaunt, it's still the established road runner you can put your faith in, day after day, run after run.

products.name: BMW Motorsport Seakers
products.details: Take the edge off your style with these PUMA Motorsport Electron E Pro sneakers. They come with an EVA midsole and a mesh upper for a lightweight, flexible feel. With a timeless look and a modern vibe, these sneakers will make a statement on any outfit.
